  fhir:text [
     fhir:status [ fhir:v "extensions" ] ;
     fhir:div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-administrative-gender.html\"><code>http://hl7.org/fhir/administrative-gender</code></a><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td><td><b><a href=\"ConceptMap-CMVFgenderIdentity.html\">VF_genderIdentity</a></b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-administrative-gender.html#administrative-gender-unknown\">unknown</a></td><td style=\"color: #cccccc\">Unknown</td><td>Unknown.</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-administrative-gender.html#administrative-gender-female\">female</a></td><td style=\"color: #cccccc\">Female</td><td>Female.</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-administrative-gender.html#administrative-gender-male\">male</a></td><td style=\"color: #cccccc\">Male</td><td>Male.</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-administrative-gender.html#administrative-gender-other\">other</a></td><td style=\"color: #cccccc\">Other</td><td>Other.</td><td/></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <code>http://va.gov/terminology/vistaDefinedTerms/2-.024</code><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b><a href=\"ConceptMap-CMVFgenderIdentity.html\">VF_genderIdentity</a></b></td></tr><tr><td>N</td><td>DOES NOT WISH TO DISCLOSE</td><td><span title=\"SOURCEISNARROWERTHANTARGET\">&lt;</span><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-administrative-gender.html#administrative-gender-unknown\">unknown</a></td></tr><tr><td>F</td><td>FEMALE</td><td><span title=\"EQUIVALENT\">~</span><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-administrative-gender.html#administrative-gender-female\">female</a></td></tr><tr><td>M</td><td>MALE</td><td><span title=\"EQUIVALENT\">~</span><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-administrative-gender.html#administrative-gender-male\">male</a></td></tr><tr><td>B</td><td>NON-BINARY</td><td><span title=\"SOURCEISNARROWERTHANTARGET\">&lt;</span><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-administrative-gender.html#administrative-gender-other\">other</a></td></tr><tr><td>O</td><td>OTHER</td><td><span title=\"EQUIVALENT\">~</span><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-administrative-gender.html#administrative-gender-other\">other</a></td></tr><tr><td>TF</td><td>TRANSGENDER FEMALE</td><td><span title=\"SOURCEISNARROWERTHANTARGET\">&lt;</span><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-administrative-gender.html#administrative-gender-other\">other</a></td></tr><tr><td>TM</td><td>TRANSGENDER MALE</td><td><span title=\"SOURCEISNARROWERTHANTARGET\">&lt;</span><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-administrative-gender.html#administrative-gender-other\">other</a></td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"
  ] ; # 
